  PERFORM C1 USING '            ENDIF.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '          ENDIF.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '        ENDIF.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '        CLEAR: CATCH_ERRNO, CATCH_T100.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '*       " Pick up rest of message without the &i.'.
