* ==============
  PERFORM C1 USING '      MOVE-CORRESPONDING ITAB TO TOUT.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '      PERFORM CHARFIELDREPL USING TOUT.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING ''.

* GENERATE: DOCNR
* ===============
