  PERFORM C1 USING '     PERFORM GETPSTCODE USING ''UNAME'' ITAB-SNAME'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '                         CHANGING TOUT-SNAME.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '     PERFORM GETPSTCODE USING ''UNAME'' ITAB-PPNAM'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '                         CHANGING TOUT-PPNAM.'.
