  PERFORM C1 USING '                         CHANGING TOUT-WWERT.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '     PERFORM GETPSTCODE USING ''TCODE'' ITAB-TCODE'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '                         CHANGING TOUT-TCODE.'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '     PERFORM GETPSTCODE USING ''WAERS'' ITAB-WAERS'.
  PERFORM C1 USING '                         CHANGING TOUT-WAERS.'.
