*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*      Form  GENABAP                                                  *
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM GENABAP.
  DATA: ERROR TYPE STRING.

  PERFORM EXPB6.
  INSERT REPORT SUBREPID FROM CODE.
  GENERATE REPORT SUBREPID MESSAGE ERROR.
  IF SY-SUBRC = 8.
    GENERROR = ABAP_TRUE.
    CONCATENATE 'Information: GENABAP error:' ERROR
                INTO CONCAT SEPARATED BY SPACE.
    CONDENSE CONCAT.
    IF WEXP-FTYPE = 'M'.
      PERFORM EXPB1REC USING WEXP-TABNAME 'E' 'C' CONCAT.
    ELSE.
      PERFORM EXPB1REC USING WEXP-TABNAME 'I' 'C' CONCAT.
    ENDIF.
  ENDIF.
  WAIT UP TO 1 SECONDS.
  COMMIT WORK AND WAIT.
ENDFORM.                    "GENABAP

